data\";s:60:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/GSXX8Hwluv0/4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Sun, 12 Jan 2014 09:30:57 PST\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"5099646@http://wordpress.org/support/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:919:\"<p>I can\'t understand why this painful white death screen have lived for ages without a death-match resolution from the Author. I am not blaming him for   making this plugin which supposed to give a breath of fresh air. Assuming..</p>\n<p>The White Screen of Death has long live for ages without pure resolution for the soul!!</p>\n<p>The same tags of frustration all over the place, but when the creator can finally end all of these sufferings cause by the system he created for mankind?!!</p>\n<p>My questions... Isn\'t it the main purpose of this creation to ease burden? If so... then why is this same \"PAIN and Soul Grieving\" persist to co exist even from the very beginning?<br />\nIs it part of the main purpose to create chaos?! if so... then</p>\n<p>LONG LIVE THE WHITE SCREEN OF DEATH! Long Live WHITE SCREEN OF DEATH!\n</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/GSXX8Hwluv0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"http://wordpress.org/support/topic/random-blank-pages-w3-total-cache/page/4#post-5099646\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"ArtGoddess on &quot;[Plugin: Infinite-Scroll] IS stops working with W3 Total Cache activated&quot;\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:105:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/N2wKaG_LMas/is-stops-working-with-w3-total-cache-activated\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Sun, 12 Jan 2014 00:49:05 PST\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"5098513@http://wordpress.org/support/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:592:\"<p>Hello!</p>\n<p>I installed Infinite Scroll and managed to set up with Canvas theme.</p>\n<p>Once I installed W3 Total Cache, and activated all functions, except minify, the infinite scroll doesn\'t work anymore, and it appears the numbers with the pages once again.</p>\n<p>Has somebody managed to get these two plugins work together?</p>\n<p>Thank you!</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/infinite-scroll/\">http://wordpress.org/plugins/infinite-scroll/</a>\n</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/N2wKaG_LMas\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\"