nal jerseys for the next 12 months.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Monmouthshire will be hosting the three biggest road championships of the year in a single week this June - two of which are being staged on a single day - plus a fantastic Championships Sportive where leisure and club riders of all ages and abilities can ride the same circuit the professionals will face.</p>'),(116,4,'_event_content','field_52d20b77b162b'),(117,20,'_wp_attached_file','the-event-bg.jpg'),(118,20,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:4:{s:5:\"width\";i:1320;s:6:\"height\";i:927;s:4:\"file\";s:16:\"the-event-bg.jpg\";s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(119,20,'_edit_lock','1389497816:1'),(120,20,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Cyclists'),(121,20,'_edit_last','1'),(122,21,'sub_title','28 - 29 June 2013 - Monmouthshire'),(123,21,'_sub_title','field_52d1f941ce7e3'),(124,21,'show_call_to_action','1'),(125,21,'_show_call_to_action','field_52d1f967ce7e4'),(126,21,'cta_button_text','Find out more'),(127,21,'_cta_button_text','field_52d1fa1ece7e8'),(128,21,'cta_link_type','page'),(129,21,'_cta_link_type','field_52d1f9a4ce7e5'),(130,21,'cta_page','2'),(131,21,'_cta_page','field_52d1f9f5ce7e6'),(132,21,'event_heading','The Event'),(133,21,'_event_heading','field_52d20b28434aa'),(134,21,'event_content','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.\r\n\r\nExcepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum. Sed ut perspiciati