t','<p style=\"text-align: right;\">The British Cycling National Road Championships is one of the UK\'s premier annual sporting events, exciting millions of bike fans across the world. 35,000 spectators enjoyed last year’s event and this year is set to be no different.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">This year, the roads of Monmouthshire will decide who will be crowned the best of Britain\'s men and women\'s racers and wear the coveted blue, red and white National jerseys for the next 12 months. Monmouthshire will be hosting the three biggest road championships of the year in a single week this June - two of which are being staged on a single day - plus a fantastic Championships Sportive where leisure and club riders of all ages and abilities can ride the same circuit the professionals will face.</p>'),(969,49,'_event_content','field_52d20b77b162b'),(970,49,'event_show_call_to_action','1'),(971,49,'_event_show_call_to_action','field_52d21774a2883'),(972,49,'event_cta_button_text','Online entry form'),(973,49,'_event_cta_button_text','field_52d21795a2884'),(974,49,'event_cta_link_type','page'),(975,49,'_event_cta_link_type','field_52d217aea2885'),(976,49,'event_cta_page','2'),(977,49,'_event_cta_page','field_52d217e5a2886'),(978,50,'sub_title','28 - 29 June 2013 - Monmouthshire'),(979,50,'_sub_title','field_52d1f941ce7e3'),(980,50,'show_call_to_action','1'),(981,50,'_show_call_to_action','field_52d1f967ce7e4'),(982,50,'cta_button_text','Find out more'),(983,50,'_cta_button_text','field_52d1fa1ece7e8'),(984,50,'cta_link_type','page'),(985,50,'_cta_link_type','field_52d1f9a4ce7e5'),(986,50,'cta_page','2'),(987,50,'_cta_page','field_52d1f9f5ce7e6'),(988,50,'maproutes_heading','Discover the beauty'),(989,50,'_maproutes_heading','field_52d22575dfb97'),(990,50,'maproutes_show_call_to_action','1'),(991,50,'_maproutes_show_call_to_action','field_52d2258fdfb98'),(992,50,'maproutes_cta_button_text','Get more info'),(993,50,'_maproutes_cta_button_text','field_52d225c6dfb